  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■ Game Description and Story ■</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Rumia Throws!</i> is a 2D stage-based action game starring <strong>Rumia</strong>, a character from the Touhou Project.<br>Rumia, too hungry to even fire danmaku, sets out to gather food by any means necessary!<br>With her powers weakened, she uses whatever she can find—boxes, rocks, fish—as weapons to throw, kick, or even ride on to move around.<br>Use a variety of creative actions to defeat enemies and secure your next meal!<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919120/extras/87f5514ac035f78a41aad032a6a08f7c.avif?t=1747926054\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919120/extras_big/87f5514ac035f78a41aad032a6a08f7c.avif?t=1747926054 width=800 height=618 /></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Punch, kick, ride...▼<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919120/extras/8f6672ecea66071e46dd54d73ec5f310.avif?t=1747926054\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919120/extras_big/8f6672ecea66071e46dd54d73ec5f310.avif?t=1747926054 width=800 height=210 /></span>■ Game System ■</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A simple action game where you use objects lying around to defeat all the enemies on the map, grab the goal item (meat), and progress through the stages one after another.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919120/extras/4964dffe1febd7e140ec12a2aad0442c.avif?t=1747926054\" width=800 height=620 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■ Variety of Actions ■</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In addition to throwing objects, you can unleash high-powered <strong>Critical Kicks</strong> to launch them with force, <strong>Parry</strong> incoming projectiles to deflect them, and use <strong>Special Moves</strong> that can only be activated when your motivation gauge is full.<br>These diverse actions open up a wide range of strategies for clearing stages.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >When the motivation gauge is filled...▼<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919120/extras/a5775cc1b2e43c2f778d522aa1e5f006.avif?t=1747926054\" width=600 height=280 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A reversal special move! It deals huge damage, but be cautious as it leaves a big opening!▼<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919120/extras/e999529756af14148adf47870ec04c99.avif?t=1747926054\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919120/extras_big/e999529756af14148adf47870ec04c99.avif?t=1747926054 width=800 height=618 /></span>Parry!!▼<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919120/extras/6ad50317e78afb0944dc7c533f5d2ac2.avif?t=1747926054\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919120/extras_big/6ad50317e78afb0944dc7c533f5d2ac2.avif?t=1747926054 width=800 height=618 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■ Various Mechanics ■ </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The items that fall each have their own unique characteristics, such as differences in flight speed, power, weight, buoyancy, flammability, and the ability to penetrate. By using them appropriately according to the situation, you may discover interesting strategies.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A wooden box that flies quickly but has low attack power, and a rock that flies slowly but has high attack power▼<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919120/extras/92bc50bdfec20dfdf033f65d7857dd5e.avif?t=1747926054\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919120/extras_big/92bc50bdfec20dfdf033f65d7857dd5e.avif?t=1747926054 width=800 height=266 /></span>There are also various weapons with different abilities▼<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919120/extras/9afa4f28ffb9a1f184ca8309885ae6ef.avif?t=1747926054\" width=800 height=550 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■<strong>Over 100 Stages!</strong>■</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each stage is divided into areas, featuring various iconic locations from Gensokyo, such as the Misty Lake and the Underground.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At the end of each area, familiar Touhou characters will appear as bosses, standing in your way.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The familiar boss of the Misty Lake, 'Cirno'▼<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919120/extras/ab5e977704e7b9a426a78f4b0386c26b.avif?t=1747926054\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919120/extras_big/ab5e977704e7b9a426a78f4b0386c26b.avif?t=1747926054 width=800 height=618 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■<strong>Another protagonist!?</strong>■</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >While this game features Rumia as the main character, you can also play as \"Kyoko Kasodani\" as a second playable character.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In addition to physical attacks with a broom, she uses sound wave attacks by shouting, and can solidify sound waves to ride or drop them, offering completely different actions compared to Rumia.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919120/extras/c114fe4f96c0dd05ba0fe0634e95d7cf.avif?t=1747926054\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919120/extras_big/c114fe4f96c0dd05ba0fe0634e95d7cf.avif?t=1747926054 width=800 height=618 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Greetings are an oasis for the soul▼<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919120/extras/7605098bc8f76b81adbe1e0c97533b20.avif?t=1747926054\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919120/extras_big/7605098bc8f76b81adbe1e0c97533b20.avif?t=1747926054 width=800 height=494 /></span>Special move: Charged Yaho!▼<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919120/extras/e24239fb1c46a40e32a40004fb842f7c.avif?t=1747926054\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919120/extras_big/e24239fb1c46a40e32a40004fb842f7c.avif?t=1747926054 width=800 height=618 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■<strong>Replayability Features</strong>■</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Clear each stage without taking damage, unlock achievements, and enjoy plenty of replayability features!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >There are a total of 40 achievements. Be sure to give them a try!▼</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919120/extras/8ba52bb92b5c38a964df89ab6b1389dc.avif?t=1747926054\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919120/extras_big/8ba52bb92b5c38a964df89ab6b1389dc.avif?t=1747926054 width=800 height=618 /></span></p>",
